GoodByeDPI-Plus
===============

This project is a derivative work of GoodbyeDPI by ValdikSS
(https://github.com/ValdikSS/GoodbyeDPI), licensed under the
Apache License, Version 2.0.

The following files were modified from the original GoodbyeDPI source:
  - src/goodbyedpi.c     — added --only-programs / --debug-proc flags
                           and per-program gate logic
  - src/Makefile          — added -liphlpapi for GetExtendedTcpTable

The following files were added:
  - src/proctrack.c       — per-program 5-tuple→PID→exe→whitelist tracker
                            with WinDivert FLOW layer integration, hot-reload
                            watcher thread, and connection seeding
  - src/proctrack.h       — public API for the per-program tracker
  - src/programs.txt      — default whitelist (editable)
  - src/start.ps1         — PowerShell launcher with DNS redirect config
  - src/install.ps1       — scheduled task installer (auto-start at logon)
  - src/uninstall.ps1     — scheduled task uninstaller
  - install.bat           — batch wrapper for install.ps1
  - uninstall.bat         — batch wrapper for uninstall.ps1
  - .github/              — GitHub Actions CI workflow and issue templates
  - README.md             — project documentation

The startup-script concept was inspired by keift/goodbyedpi
(https://github.com/keift/goodbyedpi).

WinDivert (https://github.com/basil00/Divert) by basil00 is bundled
as pre-built binaries (WinDivert.dll, WinDivert*.sys) under the
x86/ and x86_64/ directories and is used under its LGPL/MIT license.

